Step into the atelier of my artistry as I reveal the twisted tale behind sculpting my severed head. Witness the meticulous process from start to finish: Cleaning the sculpture, precisely labeling the eyes and mouth for a haunting reveal, honing the fine details that give it an unsettling realism, and finally, adding skin texture that sends shivers down your spine.
